'''莱昂纳德·阿尔弗雷德·施耐德'''（{{bd|1925年|10月13日|1966年|8月3日|}}）, 艺名'''莱尼·布鲁斯'''（Lenny Bruce），是一位美国[[单口喜剧|单口喜剧]]演员、社会批评家与[[讽刺|讽刺]]作者，以开放、即兴、具有批判性的喜剧风格而闻名。他的喜剧包含政治、宗教、性、讽刺内容、粗俗内容等元素。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bh.org.il/blog-items/fearless-politically-incorrect-lenny-bruce/|title=Let There Be Laughter – Jewish Humor Around the World|website=Beit Hatutsot|access-date=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119183729/https://www.bh.org.il/blog-items/fearless-politically-incorrect-lenny-bruce/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他在1964年的一次淫秽审判中被定罪后，于2003年被[[纽约州州长|纽约州州长]][[乔治·保陶基|乔治·保陶基]]（{{lang|en|George Pataki}}）死后追赦，这是纽约州历史上的首例。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/12/24/nyregion/no-joke-37-years-after-death-lenny-bruce-receives-pardon.html|title=No Joke! 37 Years After Death Lenny Bruce Receives Pardon|last=Kifner|first=John|date=2003-12-24|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-10-15|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506021645/https://www.nytimes.com/2003/12/24/nyregion/no-joke-37-years-after-death-lenny-bruce-receives-pardon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布鲁斯为[[1960年代反文化运动|六〇年代的反文化]]喜剧家铺平了道路。他的淫秽审判案被视为美国言论自由史上的标志性事件之一。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/12/24/nyregion/no-joke-37-years-after-death-lenny-bruce-receives-pardon.html |title=No Joke! 37 Years After Death Lenny Bruce Receives Pardon |work=Nytimes.com |date=December 24, 2003 |access-date=December 5, 2013 |first1=John |last1=Kifner |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506021645/https://www.nytimes.com/2003/12/24/nyregion/no-joke-37-years-after-death-lenny-bruce-receives-pardon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Obituary>{{cite news|last=AP|title=Obituary|url=https://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/bday/1013.html|access-date=November 28, 2011|newspaper=New York Times|date=August 4, 1966|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20011015200417/https://www.nytimes.com/learning/general/onthisday/bday/1013.html|archive-date=October 15, 2001}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/24/arts/24carlin.html | work=The New York Times | first1=Mel | last1=Watkins | first2=Bruce | last2=Weber | title=George Carlin, Comic Who Chafed at Society and Its Constraints, Dies at 71 | date=June 24, 2008 | accessdate=2021-03-17 | archive-date=2013-05-29 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gxtcrh1o?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/24/arts/24carlin.html?_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年，《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》杂志所评选的世上最伟大的五十名单口喜剧演员中，布鲁斯名列第三位（仅次于弟子[[理查德·普赖尔|理查德·普赖尔]]和[[乔治·卡林|乔治·卡林]]）。<ref>[https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/lists/50-best-stand-up-comics-of-all-time-w464199 The 50 Best Stand-up Comics of All Time] {{Wayback|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/lists/50-best-stand-up-comics-of-all-time-w464199 |date=20171211003827 }}. Rollingstone.com, retrieved February 15, 2017.</ref>

